Atlast, the wait ends, I suppose, a wonderful musical extravaganza commences, something indeed comes out from the magical box of Coke Studio.

I know, it would be hard to answer but could you please let me know the playlist and the artists being showcased during this season, curiosity killed the cat but I'll take my chances, please let me know, what music can I expect?

Whatever it be, just hit it, can hardly wait, 
And yes, my mind's itching, just gimme that musical elixir.

Missed you, anyway, see you soon.
Love - from across the borders - Oh wait... Music knows no boundaries or borders.
And I'll be seeing some from my Indian Coke Studio too....
Rejoice.... Its that time of the year.....
